          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-1" n="1">In sounds of Ioys your tunefull Voices raise</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-2" n="2">And teach the People whom to thank &amp; praise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-3" n="3">Thank Prudent Zoras providential Reign,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-4" n="4">For Peace &amp; Plenty &amp; all sorts of Grain.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-5" n="5">Thank the Stock-jobbers for your thriving Trade,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-6" n="6">Thank just Go.n that all Debts are paid.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-7" n="7">Thank the Scots P--rs for firm &amp; unbought Union.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-8" n="8">Thank B.ps for Occasional Communion.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-9" n="9">Thank Ma--ghs Zeal, who scorn'd the profer'd Treaty,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-10" n="10">And thank Eugene the French did not beat ye.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-11" n="11">Thank Whigs that vote the Church need fear no Ruin,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-12" n="12">As plain appears by what those Whigs are doing.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-13" n="13">Thank your ownselvs that you're so taxt &amp; shamm'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X84A723L-line-14" n="14">But thank th'Almighty that you are not damn'd.</l>
          </lg>
